Mark Wing-Davey is a British actor and director who portrayed the two-headed Galactic President, Zaphod Beeblebrox, in the radio and TV versions of The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy, written by Douglas Adams.

He is the son of actor and actress Peter Davey andÂ Anna Wing. Radio 
